original_title: Seventh Wonder: Welcome to Atlanta - Live 2014
overview: Seventh Wonder the Swedish Prog Metal gods, featuring current Kamelot singer Tommy Karevik - release their first live product ever, with a full rendition of their masterpiece album Mercy Falls and a selection of their most popular material. Recorded live at ProgPower USA on September 2014.
title: Seventh Wonder: Welcome to Atlanta - Live 2014
